GWADAR, Mar 9 (APP): Participants at a seminar held at the University of Gwadar here on Thursday stressed on the need for reconciliation process to address the issues faced by the people of Balochistan.
Speaking at the seminar titled Reconciliation in Balochistan, they asked the militants and exiled leaders to come to the negotiating table and resolve issues through talks.The Speakers included Hussain Ashraf of the National Party, Vice Chancellor of University of Gwadar Abdul Razaq Sabir and Additional Deputy Commissioner Zakir Baloch.
